nude on the moon is a 1961 &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; nudist film co-written and co-directed by doris wishman and raymond phelan under the shared pseudonyms " o. o. miller " and " anthony brooks " . the film was produced in 1960 and theatrically released in 1961 . nude on the moon is the second of eight nudist films produced and directed by wishman . while most nudist films of the time were set within a conventional nudist camp , apparently as a promotional gimmick wishman decided to set the story in a nudist civilization on the moon .